node.text:
This is really close to my heart. So many things have changed in the past year. And while I look forward to the Olympic Games, I know it is still a very challenging time for everyone out there. I am so proud to be part of @SKII STUDIO latest film #BeyondTheStadium which shines a spotlight on female entrepreneurs that have been hit hard by the pandemic.

Growing-up with a female entrepreneur myself (MOM ♥) I am thrilled to see that on top of the launch of the film, comes the 1st #ChangeDestiny Fund program in support of this community in Tokyo. Much to feel happy about - watch to learn how you can help too. #SKIIPARTNER

node.text: Dreams come true.💫Thank you @athleta and @area for my custom dress for the #MetGala and this unforgettable memory! As a young girl, I never dreamt I'd be here. As a guest of Athleta, I wanted to make sure that as a part of the night, we were also giving back—and that all the girls out there know they can dream big, too. To celebrate, Athleta is donating $50,000 to The Power of She Fund to empower women and girls. This is for you, girls! #PowerOfShe #AthletaPartner #MetInAmerica

node.text: Athleta Presents Gold Over America Tour kicks off September 21 in Tucson. Starring an all-star team of champion gymnasts. Visit goldoveramericatour.com for tickets and details. @Athleta @goldoveramericatour

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Simone Biles on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text:
🤸🏾‍♀️Giveaway! 🤸🏾‍♀️ To celebrate the @goldoveramerica tour kick-off, I’m partnering with @athleta to give away tickets for you and your bestie to see me and my girls perform! Can’t wait to see y’all there! Now here’s how to enter for a chance to win :
 
💛 Like this post 
💛 Follow @athleta, @Simonebiles, and @goldoveramericatour
💛 Tag a friend you want to see the tour with and comment which city you’d like to attend! For a list of cities, please click the link in my bio to see rules. #athletapartner
 
For another entry, head over to @athleta and @goldoveramerica and like their sweepstakes posts––you can comment on each post up to two times, for a total of six chances to win!
 
Winners will be contacted by @athleta via DM. NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Legal residents of the 50 United States (D.C.) 18 +. Enter by 9/9/21 at noon ET. See Official Rules, for odds and prize details at goldoveramericatour.com/goat/sweepstakes. Winners are be solely responsible for transportation and any accommodations required to attend this event. Void where prohibited.

node.text:
can’t believe it’s already been a month. 

Definitely not the way I planned the olympics going but I wouldn’t change anything for the world 🤎 I’m proud of myself and the career I’ve had thus far. this olympics doesn’t erase the past accomplishments I’ve achieved nor does it define who I am as an athlete. I’ve pushed through so much the past couple years , the word quitter is not in my vocabulary. for some of you that may be how you define me but keep talking because I can’t hear you over my 7 olympic medals which tied me for the most decorated gymnast EVER as well as most decorated american gymnast 😊🤭

node.text: I'm so proud to partner with @livecandid, who just donated $10,000 on my behalf to @thelovelandfoundation - an amazing organization that connects Black women and girls to therapy and counseling support. The donation will fund 83 therapy sessions and shows just how committed Candid is to helping people prioritize their health and live as their true, authentic selves. #Candidpartner
